  "name": "Déjà Vu II: Lost in Las Vegas",
  "shortName": "dj-vu-ii-lost-in-las-vegas",
  "description": "<i>Déjà Vu II: Lost in Las Vegas</i> is the sequel to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=D%c3%a9j%c3%a0+Vu%3a+A+Nightmare+Comes+True\">Déjà Vu: A Nightmare Comes True</a>. This time you wake up in Las Vegas with great headache and realize that you are Ace Harding, who has to find $112,000 of recently murdered Chicago's racketeer Joey Siegel for his boss and Las Vegas' mobster Tony Malone. You have a choice to find money in one week or classical &quot;or else&quot;. Just for formality you are watched by Malone's thug Stogie Martin.<br><br>During the investigation in Noir style you can collect and use items, talk to characters and make some decisions. The game has a multiple windows interface, which size and position you can change.\n",
